graph LR
    GIT[Git Push] -->|Webhook| JENKINS[Jenkins]
    JENKINS --> TESTS[Tests pytest]
    TESTS -->|PASS| BUILD[Build Images Parallel]
    TESTS -->|FAIL| SLACK[Slack Alert]
    BUILD --> SCAN[Trivy Scan]
    SCAN -->|CRITICAL| SLACK
    SCAN -->|PASS| PUSH[Push to Hub]
    PUSH --> HELM[Update Helm]
    HELM --> STRATEGY{Deployment Strategy}
    STRATEGY -->|Canary| CANARY[Canary 5 to 100]
    STRATEGY -->|Blue-Green| BLUEGREEN[Blue-Green Instant Switch]
    STRATEGY -->|Rolling| ROLLING[Rolling One-by-One]
    CANARY -->|Monitor Metrics| PROM[Prometheus]
    BLUEGREEN -->|Health Check| HEALTH[Health Checks]
    ROLLING -->|Verify| HEALTH
    PROM -->|Error Rate over 1 percent| ROLLBACK[Rollback]
    PROM -->|Error Rate below 1 percent| NEXT[Next Stage]
    NEXT -->|Traffic 100 percent| COMPLETE[Complete]
    ROLLBACK --> SLACK
    HEALTH -->|Pass| SLACK2[Slack Notify]
    COMPLETE --> SLACK2
